episodes.title: GRAND ZERO | comedy/thriller short film
episodes.description:
It's not a cult. It's America. A family man returns to his hometown to discover he's the last person in town who's not part of a massive pyramid scheme. And everyone-- EVERYONE-- wants him in.

starring Brian Huskey, Janie Haddad Tompkins, Lexi Ainsworth, Thomas Lennon, Ian Roberts
written and directed by Kevin Oeser 
produced by Divide/Conquer
